title: Men In Black The Animated Series Season 1
description:
Based on the blockbuster films, Men in Black: The Animated Series chronicles the further adventures of agents Jay and Kay.
Along with their colleagues, Zed and Elle, they provide intergalactic, top-secret security services to guard the earth from extraterrestrial evil-doers. With firepower and attitude to burn, agents Jay and Kay pursue their mission to protect the earth from the scum of the universe.

Special features:None.
